title: New Yankee Workshop - 1999 Season Episode 5 - Teak Bar
description:
New Yankee Workshop - 1999 Season Episode 5 - Teak Bar. 


This episode is no longer for sale and has been discontinued on the New Yankee Workshop website.  So I guess it is now obsolete.  I am beginning to think that maybe Norm didn&#039;t like his 1999 season.  However, as usual, Norm produces one good show.  It is in avi format, from a british source. If you like it, be sure to buy other tapes/dvd/plans from Norm at newyankee.com
